Basic Installation
==================

Here are the instructions to build the cliphist2 application
for all supported platforms.

  a) Mac OS X (for Qt 4.x), tested: Mac OS X 10.6
  b) Linux Desktop (for Qt 4.x), tested: Ubuntu 9.04 and SuSE 11.1
  c) Windows Desktop (for Qt 4.x, mingw), tested: Windows XP Home

This release supports only Qt4 (tested with 4.5.3 and 4.6.0).

Build with qmake:
-----------------
Unpack the source code into a directory, enter this directory and run:

  qmake -r cliphist2.pro
  make                      # for linux and Mac
 or:
  mingw32-make              # for windows 
